'''''From a Whisper''''' ni firime yikinamico yo [[Kenya|muri Kenya]] yanditswe kandi iyobowe  Wanuri Kahiu<ref>From A Whisper | African Film Festival, Inc. (africanfilmny.org)</ref> . Iyi filime yakiriye nomination 12 kandi yatsindiye ibihembo 5 muri African Movie Academy Awards muri 2009<ref>From a Whisper - Variety <nowiki>https://variety.com</nowiki> › film › from-a-whisper-1117943881</ref>, harimo ''Ishusho'' Nziza, ''Amajwi Yumwimerere''  '', Umuyobozi'' mwiza, ''Amashusho yumwimerere meza'' na ''AMAA Achievement muguhindura''<ref>From a Whisper (2009) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › from-a-whisper</ref> .  Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye igihembo ''cyiza cyo kwerekana inkuru nziza'' mu iserukiramuco rya Pan African Film &amp;amp; Arts 2010<ref>Films by Wanuri Kahiu <nowiki>https://www.trigon-film.org</nowiki> › directors › Wanuri_Kahiu</ref>,  kandi ihabwa igihembo cya BAFTA / LA ''Festival Choice'' Award 2010<ref>"From A Whisper" By Wanuri Kahiu With Tsitsi Dangarembga ... <nowiki>https://www.africavenir.org</nowiki> › news-details › article › afr...</ref>.  Nubwo iyi filime yibuka isabukuru yimyaka 10 ry’iterabwoba ryabaye ku ya 7 Kanama muri Kenya mu 1998<ref>From a Whisper :: Black Studies Program - Swarthmore College <nowiki>https://www.swarthmore.edu</nowiki> › black-studies-program</ref>, ntabwo ivuga ku gisasu cy’iterabwoba. Iyi filime yerekana inkuru ifatika y’inyuma y’icyo gisasu<ref>Terrorism in Kenya: Remembering the 1998 United States ... <nowiki>https://www.boell.de</nowiki> › educulture › africa-interview-W...</ref>, ifata ubuzima bw’abahohotewe n’imiryango yabo bagombaga gutora ibice by’ubuzima bwabo byangijwe n’icyo gisasu.<ref>"From A Whisper" By Wanuri Kahiu With Tsitsi Dangarembga ... <nowiki>https://www.africavenir.org</nowiki> › news-details › article › afr...</ref>  

